{"title":"自定义hexo new生成的文章布局","uid":"1bc722ba49f8fbf6413408f663883fcd","slug":"自定义hexo new生成的文章布局","date":"2023-02-24T11:25:12.000Z","updated":"2023-02-24T11:41:27.145Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/自定义hexo new生成的文章布局.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<p>命令行输入”hexo n 文件名”后会自动生成一个.md文件<br>文件开头的布局可以自定义<br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/strange-id/img@master/202302241927637.png\"></p>\n<p>在scaffolds文件夹中有三种布局，默认使用post布局创建新文章<br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/strange-id/img@master/202302241929321.png\"></p>\n<p>更改post布局即可</p>\n<h2 id=\"出现其他问题\"><a href=\"#出现其他问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"出现其他问题\"></a>出现其他问题</h2><p>报错：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/strange-id/img@master/202302241935305.png\"></p>\n<p>本来以为是中文名的问题，改成英文也不行，注释掉作者行就好了。可能是这个主题没有对应的author？或者是因为已经默认设置过了作者名？暂时没找到原因。反正也用不着，不管了。</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"命令行输入”hexo n 文件名”后会自动生成一个.md文件文件开头的布局可以自定义 在scaffolds文件夹中有三种布局，默认使用post布局创建新文章 更改post布局即可 出现其他问题报错： 本来以为是中文名的问题，改成英文也不行，注释掉作者行就好了。可能是这个主题没有对...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":187,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"学习记录","slug":"学习记录","count":5,"path":"api/categories/学习记录.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"小技巧","slug":"小技巧","count":4,"path":"api/tags/小技巧.json"},{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","count":2,"path":"api/tags/hexo.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\">出现其他问题</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"这id好怪","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"记录学业、生活、爱好","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"配置环境变量","uid":"a1f4f66b45c38bdb62cbf9732ce10bcf","slug":"配置环境变量","date":"2023-02-24T06:30:13.000Z","updated":"2023-02-24T06:39:44.438Z","